	<div class="gk-right">
		<h2>Rules of engagement</h2>
		<ol>
			<li>No university or production system attacks. My colleagues or university don't like being attacked and may prosecute</li>
			<li>One pay-out per day</li>
			<li>One pay-out per vulnerability</li>
			<li>Full disclosure required</li>
			<li>No leaving known attack vectors behind after the attack</li>
			<li>Don't violate my privacy, make GPG signatures in my name, etc. Follow common sense</li>
		</ol>
		<hr>
		<h2>No physical violence!</h2>
		<p>Beating me up or threatening with physical violence is not
		fair game. Blackmailing or physically stealing my laptop or
		computer from my hands while I'm using it is also not
		allowed.</p>
		<p>My phone and computers are logged in to Facebook, Twitter
		and Gmail. If you manage to find them unlocked, you'll be able
		to retrieve the treasures.</p>
		<h2>No break-ins!</h2>
		<p>I have not secured my home against physical break-ins.
		Don't break into my house for these bounties. It's okay if I
		let you in.</p>
